		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Courtney E. Martin</span></strong> is the author of <em>Perfect Girls, Starving Daughters: The Frightening New Normalcy of Hating Your Body</em> (Free Press). She is currently assisting Marvelyn S. Brown, a twenty-three-year-old <span class="smallcaps">AIDS</span> activist, with her memoir, to be published later this year. She lives in Brooklyn, New York.</p><a href="/contributors/courtney-e-martin" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
